 href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Amir-Hossein-Maghsoudloo-known-professionally-as-Amir-Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Amir-Hossein-Maghsoudloo-known-professionally-as-Amir-Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Amir-Hossein-Maghsoudloo-known-professionally-as-Amir-Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Amir-Hossein-Maghsoudloo-known-professionally-as-Amir-Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Amir-Hossein-Maghsoudloo-known-professionally-as-Amir-Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Amir-Hossein-Maghsoudloo-known-professionally-as-Amir-Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Amir-Hossein-Maghsoudloo-known-professionally-as-Amir-Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>流行歌手塔塔卢被判亵渎罪后，伊朗法院在上诉中判处他死刑。</p><p>据当地报纸<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/iran-tataloo-death-sentence-blasphemy-b2682562.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Etemad》</em></a>报道，“最高法院接受了检察官的反对意见”，以亵渎罪判处五年监禁。它接着说，“案件重新审理，这次被告因侮辱先知而被判处死刑”，指的是伊斯兰教的先知穆罕默德。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2025/jan/19/iranian-court-sentences-pop-star-tataloo-to-death-for-blasphemy?CMP=fb_gu#Echobox=1737321101" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道，该判决并非最终判决，仍可上诉。</p><p> Tataloo（真名 Amir Hossein Maghsoudloo）在被伊朗当局多次逮捕且未能获得文化和伊斯兰指导部的音乐活动许可证后，于 2018 年移居伊斯坦布尔。</p><p> 2023 年 12 月，土耳其警方将他移交给伊朗，此后他一直被拘留在伊朗。 </p><figure id="attachment_3830306" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830306" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830306" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tataloo.-CREDIT_-HAMED-BADIEE_Middle-East-Images_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830306" class="wp-caption-text">塔塔卢。图片来源：HAMED BADIEE/中东图片/法新社盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>他还因宣扬“卖淫”而被判处 10 年徒刑，并在其他案件中被指控传播反对伊斯兰共和国的“宣传”和发布“淫秽内容”。</p><p>这位以纹身外貌闻名的地下歌手于 2011 年发行了首张专辑《Zire Hamkaf》。此后，他发行了 21 张专辑，其中包括 2021 年的《Fereshteh》，这张专辑使他成为首位与环球音乐集团合作的伊朗音乐家。</p><p>此前，他曾被保守派政客利用，试图接触年轻、自由的伊朗人。 2017年，他与保守派伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西举行了电视会议，2015年，他发行了一首支持伊朗核计划的歌曲。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iranian-court-sentences-pop-singer-tataloo-to-death-for-blasphemy-3830284">伊朗法院以亵渎罪判处流行歌手 Tataloo 死刑的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
