了“One Guitar”，并与 Joe Grushecky 和 ​​Houserockers 一起演奏了“Never Be Enough Time”。</p><p>随后，他继续演奏了一系列自己的热门歌曲，包括《城镇边缘的黑暗》、《应许之地》、《粉红凯迪拉克》，以及他为琼·杰特创作的与该活动同名的《Light Of Day》和迈克尔·J·福克斯 1987 年的同名电影。看看下面的视频。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="杰西·马林 (Jesse Malin) ft. 布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) - 现场 |损坏的收音机 - LOD 25 @ Count Basie, Red Bank NJ 1/18/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ucy_O9lXdh8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀和威利·尼罗 - 一把吉他" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wkqBwp3M1-s?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 - 现场 |黑暗 - 白天之光 2025 @ Count Basie Theater, Red Bank NJ 1/18/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/w46qIfynY7Q?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 - 现场 | Savin’ Up - Light of Day 2025 @ Count Basie Theater, Red Bank NJ 1/18/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UDmFzpYEENs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Pumping Iron- Bruce Springsteen Joe Grushecky The Houserockers - Light Of Day 2025" width="696" height="392" src="http