 André 3000 等人在新合辑中分享未发行的音乐，以援助洛杉矶野火受害者https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-and-more-share-unreleased-music-in-new-compilation-album-to-aid-la-wildfires-victims-3830253?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=andre-3000-and-more-share-unreleased-music-in-new-compilation-album-to-aid-la-wildfires-受害者Surej SinghMon, 20 Jan 2025 08:11:48 +0000 Music NewsNewsExperimentalIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3830253 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Leaving Records 的 98 首曲目合辑还包括 Julia Holter、Steve Roach、Reggie Watts 等</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-and-more-share-unreleased-music-in-new-compilation-album-to-aid-la-wildfires-victims-3830253">André 3000 等人在新合辑中分享了未发行的音乐，以援助洛杉矶野火受害者，</a>该专辑首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/andre-3000@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont